author: Bryant Hevesi For Daily Mail Australia
title: The Vietnamese man who became a gang's meth 'tester boy' | Daily Mail Online
text: From poor street kid to $20K-a-week drug dealer with such taste for meth he became the feared 5T gang's DRUG TESTER Johnny Nguyen spent a decade dealing, abusing drugs such as ice and heroin He associated with members of Sydney's notorious Vietnamese gang 5T In his prime, Mr Nguyen was raking in almost $20,000 from his drug dealing He was taking seven grams of the drug ice a week, which equated to $2,000 Mr Nguyen has now turned his life around and speaks at events around Australia
